Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}首先買點東西填飽肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏要蘋果糖 巧克力香蕉和章魚燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好可惜啊 今天肚子只夠吃這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}糟了 差點忘了買棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別這麼硬撐著吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不懂風情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}祭典裡吃棉花糖的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就跟洗完澡後冰淇淋的可口一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此 那我也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}店在那邊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}最近的棉花糖 顏色都好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}接下來要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥 我想去抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}拉繩子的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抽籤？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒一根繩子是能中獎的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不去試試怎麼會中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}絕對只是浪費錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎…
