Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}心臟會突然揪成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好閒啊 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還想說今年花季那麼早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}客人應該挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看來是我猜錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我的目標不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}最近好運連連呀 我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好運檔都檔不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.66,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她剛剛抽中籤 很想炫耀一番
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥還說抽不中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但我一次就中了 厲害吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你可以占卜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對 如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}阿圭 我能體驗學習一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這個啊…沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}拜託你了 請幫我占卜一下未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就先從姓名占卜開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請在這裡寫上自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}占卜師也是女生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼要打扮成這樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}因為看起來比較像占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比你大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼要當占卜師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}因為我會占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我可以摸摸這隻老鼠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不行 還有牠是倉鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是小紅帽嗎 問東問西的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了 這樣就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}木幡真琴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是想占卜未來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就讓我來占卜一…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這一刻終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我的未來究竟發生什麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為…為了讓占卜更加準確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還需要你多寫一條訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就先把電話號碼 郵遞區號 住址
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}家庭結構 血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}寫上所有你能想到的關於自己的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這我實在不能答應…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害的占卜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是占卜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對啊…對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}從常理來看是不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我就問個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是木幡茜的妹妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我的姐姐就叫茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了 太好了太好了太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請問…結果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我一開始就沒在占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.03,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用掩飾了 我也是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 五年前來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那你就是真琴的前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒想到能在這裡碰上魔女前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能跟你交個朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別和我攀關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}木幡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}告訴你一年前發生的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}去年櫻花祭上發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養在占卜啊 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過是路邊攤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}慢慢有點起色了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好評不少 說我占卜挺準的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下次你也來吧 我幫你占卜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}表面上說是占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}其實背後有耍小把戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過難得見你會來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是妹妹好像也想當魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很有可能會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以我提前來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}如果見到我妹妹 麻煩你多多照顧喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 當然啊 這點小事包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你喝多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 雖然算不上謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}讓你看看我新創作的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很厲害的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的喔 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是說你們喝了個痛快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我就是因為木幡茜她一時興起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}才變成了這副可憎的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這副身體…要怎麼賠我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但這可是貨真價實的魔法藥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有朋友委託 我就試做了幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 有什麼效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}人吃了之後會變成動物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 這個魔法相當困難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像是呢 但試了一下居然就做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你果然是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}像你這個年紀的魔女可沒幾個能做到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過呢 還不知道究竟有沒有效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養 你要不要吃一個試試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你這是開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}頭好痛 果然喝不了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:56.70,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}茜 茜 茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是去年的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐的藥讓你變成這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那傢伙喝得很醉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肯定是她胡鬧 塞進我嘴裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還好那個藥不算完成品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以太陽下山後能變回人類的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但都怪這個藥 我的個人生活變得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別摸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你和我姐姐是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}老朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但她從以前就一直在世界各地到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}根本抓不到她在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只是猜她可能還會回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以就在這裡擺攤占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}於是她的妹妹 你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抱歉剛剛對你大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是驚訝到腦袋一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不會 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是太好了 我終於能解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}身為她的妹妹 你總知道怎麼連絡上她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}手機號碼也好 能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐她沒有手機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}家裡也沒有人知道她在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽 我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎回來 真是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這位是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是位可愛的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是千夏的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 她叫犬養
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我是千夏的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}女兒受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倒茶倒茶~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴姐要你在這裡等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你媽媽完全不吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}聽說年紀大了 就不容易吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我找找…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}試試看這個吧 說不定有辦法恢復喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}讓動物變成人類外表的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要給我用這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是的 我會用跟姐姐相反的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用了 茜回來的時候告訴我一聲就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒人知道姐姐她什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有 姐姐犯下的錯就是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請讓我負起責任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是這個魔法看起來也好困難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題的 我可沒抱著「趁機學習」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}或者「早就想試一試」的輕浮心態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像魔女呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 確實像個魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我本來就是魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}最後加一滴這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看起來像金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}吃了就能復原嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}並不能完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是吃下去就能暫時恢復人類的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以你白天也能保持人類的模樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總比束手無策要好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題的 肯定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}變得更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對不起 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你只吃了一顆 應該馬上就能變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了 恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}雖然沒有完全恢復人形…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒關係啦 你又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但要變回人類 似乎還有很長的路要走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐回來的話 我會第一時間通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請再等待一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她大概什麼時候會回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她前幾天才回來了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也不好說下次會是什麼時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎…只能耐著性子等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}並不是你的錯 別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過你們姐妹可真不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}經常聽人這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我倒是覺得很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}特別是長得漂亮這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是我不該亂說啦 對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 話說你在這裡做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}去年不是說要幫我占卜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抽空去了祭典會場一趟又找不到你人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只好一個人逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 要吃章魚燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼一見面就得聽你抱怨？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}都是你亂搞 我才變成這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你可知道我受了多少苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不是你自作自受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養 你喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}和你喝酒太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不小心喝太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咬什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}木籤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}茜 我要小吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抱歉 沒有錢了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就用魔法做吧 拿葉片什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我會被抓的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你帶巧克力了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說什麼啊 剛剛不是向我推薦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的不能吃啊 會變成動物的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我叫犬養嘛 所以有時也得學點狗的樣子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你說什麼莫名其妙的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看起來真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.00,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不行 不行不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}到了早上 你看見自己的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我好像還非常興奮…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然後又睡著了 我怎麼叫都叫不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這能恢復嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}短時間不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是藥效總有一天會過的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用太心急的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}給你們添大麻煩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我也有在找還原的方法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}找到了就通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養小姐 你的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 已經晚上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這才是我真實的容貌 可別忘了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎再來 犬養小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 再見 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是我喜歡的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}可愛到讓人有點生氣呀 好嫉妒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我得節制點喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下次要去鄭重道個歉
